            <div class="show-for-medium-up project-details">              
              <p class="detail-text">
                Great Green Sources is a nationwide wholesale nursery distributor built on creating and maintaining close personal relationships. Part of that process is providing timely information on product availabilities, and introducing customers to a hand picked list of vendors and their products. 
              </p>
              <p class="detail-text">
                Mobility is a key feature of the site, as Great Green Sources customers are rarely at a desktop. Thus, the site was designed with a mobile first approach, interchanging content based on the context. 
              </p>              
              <a href="https://github.com/timsvoice/great_green_sources" class="small button secondary">View Source</a>
